headline: Plan Sponsors Reaffirm Commitment to Workforce Retirement Benefits, According to New MetLife Study
summary: NEW YORK, March 31, 2025--Despite a constantly evolving macroeconomic landscape, plan sponsors remain firmly committed to providing workforce retirement benefits for the foreseeable future. MetLife’s 2025 Enduring Retirement Model Study, released today, found that eight in ten (82%) of plan sponsors cannot envision a time when their company would no longer offer any retirement benefits.
